subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Despite faltering in the second set, Madison Keys, 19, defeated Klara Koukalova, 7-6, 6-7 (3), 6-2, on Thursday to advance to the third round at Wimbledon.
